Web UI compressor 0.3.4-SNAPSHOT API

Packages
com.github.wuic This package is the most general package of the WUIC library.
com.github.wuic.configuration  
com.github.wuic.configuration.impl This package contains different POJO which could be used to represent the Configuration implementations.
com.github.wuic.engine This package contains the definition of an Engine.
com.github.wuic.engine.impl.ehcache This package contains the engines which are based on the EhCache framework.
com.github.wuic.engine.impl.embedded This package contains the engines which don't delegate its work to any library like YUI Compressor.
com.github.wuic.engine.impl.yuicompressor This package contains the engines which are based on the YUI Compressor library.
com.github.wuic.exception This package contains all common exceptions which could be thrown by WUIC.
com.github.wuic.exception.wrapper This packages defines exceptions which wrap or represent a particular and common exception.
com.github.wuic.exception.xml This package contains all exceptions related to wuic.xml path.
com.github.wuic.factory This package contains all the classes that transparently create the Engine implementations.
com.github.wuic.factory.impl This package contains all the factory classes which provide Engine implementations.
com.github.wuic.ftp  
com.github.wuic.gstorage This package defines required implementation for resource stored in a S3 AWS.
com.github.wuic.resource This package defines what is a resource in WUIC.
com.github.wuic.resource.impl This package defines different implements of a WuicResource.
com.github.wuic.resource.impl.classpath This package defines required implementation for resource stored in the classpath.
com.github.wuic.resource.impl.disk This package defines required implementation for resource stored on the disk.
com.github.wuic.resource.impl.http This package defines required implementation for resource stored over HTTP.
com.github.wuic.s3 This package defines required implementation for resource stored in a S3 AWS.
com.github.wuic.servlet This package defines the Servlet support provided by WUIC.
com.github.wuic.ssh  
com.github.wuic.tag This package defines the tags provided by WUIC.
com.github.wuic.util Utility package where helper methods are defined.
com.github.wuic.util.path This package defines a little API used by WUIC to resolve a hierarchical path with each element corresponding to either a path, a directory, a ZIP archive or an entry of a ZIP archive.
com.github.wuic.xml This package provides the classes which read the 'wuic.xml' path.
